# Appellate Style (Oregon Law Library Exemplars)

Model briefs from:
- CA: cdm17027.contentdm.oclc.org/p17027coll8
- SC: cdm17027.contentdm.oclc.org/p17027coll7

**Structure (ORAP-based):**
- Caption (court/parties/case #)
- Table of Contents/Authorities
- Questions Presented
- Statement of Facts (record cites)
- Argument (I. Issue; A. Rule; B. Record; C. Application)
- Conclusion (relief requested)
- Certificate of Compliance

Prose: Restrained, rule-application heavy. No ad hominem.
